'''國家路易斯大學'''（'''National Louis University'''，縮寫：'''NLU'''）是位於[[美國|美國]][[伊利諾伊州|伊利諾伊州]][[芝加哥|芝加哥]]的一所[[私立大學|私立大學]]，成立於1886年。<ref name="encyclopedia.chicagohistory.org">{{cite web |url=http://www.encyclopedia.chicagohistory.org/pages/2182.html |title=National-Louis University |work=The Electronic Encyclopedia of Chicago |publisher=Chicago Historical Society |year=2005 |accessdate=2011-09-06 |archive-date=2018-08-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180803194254/http://www.encyclopedia.chicagohistory.org/pages/2182.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 除去在芝加哥[[盧普區|盧普區]]的主校區外，在[[威斯康辛州|威斯康辛州]]、[[佛羅里達州|佛羅里達州]]和波蘭的[[新松奇|新松奇]]還有數個校區，此外也提供遠程教育。<ref>Snyder, Agnes. 1972. Dauntless Women in Childhood Education, 1856 - 1931. Washington, D.C.: Association for Childhood Education International. p. 98</ref><ref>"Early Childhood Education: Preparation of Teachers." Encyclopedia of Education. The Gale Group, Inc, 2002. Retrieved, 27 Jul. 2010 from http://www.answers.com/topic/early-childhood-education-preparation-of-teachers {{Wayback|url=http://www.answers.com/topic/early-childhood-education-preparation-of-teachers |date=20150621033134 }}</ref>
2015年《[[美國新聞與世界報道|美國新聞與世界報道]]》未將其列入排名。<ref>{{cite web|title=National Louis University|url=http://colleges.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/best-colleges/national-louis-university-1733|publisher=U.S. News and World Report|accessdate=2015-03-08|archive-date=2015-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150407070418/http://colleges.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/best-colleges/national-louis-university-1733|dead-url=no}}</ref>

